posting_body: ['Highly underpriced 1 Bedroom Apartment on Corey Street in West Roxbury', 'Location is Impressive!', 'Highly sought after section of West Roxbury', 'Very close to Centre St, VFW Parkway, numerous restaurants and more', 'Only 6 minute walk to Commuter Rail T', 'Available for 8/1/2022 move in', 'Beautiful second floor apartment featuring: Big eat in kitchen, dining room / dining alcove, large living room, great bonus sun room or office off of the kitchen.', 'Gleaming hardwood floors, high ceilings.', 'Dishwasher', 'Newer Fridge', 'Newer gas stove', 'Very easy street parking', 'Shared deck', 'Modern Bathroom with a beautiful modern vanity', 'Ample closet space', 'Laundry in building', 'Utilities are not included', 'Very Rare Listing, will not find anything similar for this price', 'For showings, email patrick @ <URL> (no spaces) or text your email address to 508.243.5319', 'If interested please: when reaching out include a brief description, what you do for work, etc.', 'Patrick Gray', 'Metro Realty Corp', '508-243-5319', 'Also, feel free to check out my Youtube Channel for full video walkthroughs of several apartments in Boston, Brighton, Brookline and more.', 'New videos are added frequently, copy and paste link below or search Patrick Gray Real Estate on Youtube', 'https www youtube com channel UCdhMp_yHF3SmPQ8YS4-b9kQ']
